item.description: We had a lot of fun last week at the dog park in Hooksett. We'll be going back this friday morning. When the school year begins, we'll be trying a weeknight. I'm going to try for a weekly trip to the park, hopefully on the same day so people can plan for it. Also, I need to update my photos. My boyfriend and I have two wonderful Labradors, Fenway Frankenstein (5yrs) and Chumlee Dogzilla (5mos). :)
